data.description:
Recent price reduction reflects seller motivation.

Seller also willing to contribute up to $10,000 toward closing costs or rate buy downs.  

WELCOME HOME to a gorgeous 4-bedroom, 2 bath home featuring 10-foot tray ceilings, crown molding and an open floor plan - perfect for entertaining.  The large yard provides a serene retreat and room for chickens or other small animals.  Plant enthusiasts welcome!  Enjoy banana trees in several varieties, a tangerine tree, pineapple plants, plumerias, birds of paradise, oak trees and palms.  Corian countertops, tile backsplash and 2-year-old stainless steel appliances give this kitchen a clean, modern feel.  New flooring installed in main living areas in 2018.  This turnkey home is ready for memories that will last a lifetime!
